                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1551" type="given" value="ALEXANDER"></interp>ALEXANDER TAHOURDIN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable L</hi> 57.) I was at Mr. Sandwell's on the evening of the 4th, and took the prisoner—I found nothing on him—I produce two half-crowns which Sandwell gave me.</p>
